data.description: Welcome to this captivating single family home situated at 12430 Jacobs Pond in the sought-after neighborhood of Villages of West Creek. This property offers a unique Spanish style that sets it apart from other homes in the area. Upon entering, you will be greeted by a beautifully designed open kitchen boasting granite countertops, providing the perfect space for entertaining family and friends. The layout of this home is meticulously designed to offer both functionality and comfort. With four spacious bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, there is room for everyone to relax and unwind. In addition to the exceptional interior features, this property offers an abundance of outdoor space for you to enjoy. Whether you want to soak up the sun on the deck, have a barbecue with friends, or simply relax in the peaceful backyard, you will find it all here. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this unique, Spanish-style single family home in the desirable neighborhood of Villages of West Creek. Close to Lackland AFB
